Text: It seems one blink away and we are at the end of this project.
There are three goals which I set up at the very beginning.
Although I did not perfectly accomplish all of them, I did learn a fantastic amount.
I came into it with a rarely knowledge, but this opened up a lot of areas that I did not have much exposure to.
Learning how to code is like a magician performs magic tricks.
